name: Best of the Robot of the Month Club
description:
Twelve scintillating robot prints delivered to your door. Be surprised every month with a robot image from the Robot of the Month club. The Robot of the Month club was a subscription print club that ran from January 2008-December 2013 and featured 72 original robot images.

For $100, each month you will receive a 5"x7" print of an original robot painting-- a whole year of robot art. The images are scanned from the original gouache paintings and printed using a 6-color giclee process on Strathmore Artist Paper.

Prints are shipped flat in a plastic sleeve in a cardboard mailer via snail mail. Price includes domestic shipping! Prints are sent out the first week of every month from Seattle, Washington, Robot Capital of the World!
